+All tests pass. The implementation is ready.
+
+We have:
+- `solveToggle` using meet-in-the-middle to handle up to 40 buttons efficiently.
+- `solveCounter` using Gaussian elimination over GF(modulus) with free variable iteration and local search for high nullity.
+
+The code is in `/workspace/src/index.ts` and compiled to `/workspace/dist/index.js`.
+
+We can now mark the task as complete.
